description:
This week's episode goes undercover, as we look at Hitman with io Interactive creative director Christian Elverdam.

Jonny Robot lets his retro fanboy freak fly as he chats to Capcom about Mega-Man: Legacy Collection (the first six games starring the Blue Bomber, all restored beautifully for a modern release).

And we navigate the dangerous waters of new expansion Civilization: Beyond Earth - Rising Tide, trying to keep our feet dry with some help from Firaxis.

...plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news as well - this is Player Attack!
